    HsQML-based implementation of Nine Men's Morris

Executable hsqml-morris
    Default-language: Haskell2010
    Hs-source-dirs: src
    Main-is: Morris/Main.hs
    Other-modules:
        Morris.Main
        Morris.Board
    Build-depends:
        base       == 4.*,
        containers >= 0.4 && < 0.6,
        deepseq    >= 1.2 && < 1.4,
        directory  >= 1.1 && < 1.3,
        tagged     >= 0.4 && < 0.8,
        OddWord    == 1.0.*,
        hsqml      == 0.2.*

